variants universal portdir sysutils/apt-dater description {Remotely install/upgrade packages on systems using apt, rug or yum package managers} homepage http://www.ibh.de/apt-dater/ epoch 0 platforms darwin name apt-dater depends_lib {port:glib2 port:libxml2 port:ncurses port:popt} long_description {apt-dater provides an ncurses frontend for managing package updates on a large number of remote hosts using SSH. It supports Debian-based managed hosts as well as rug (e.g. openSUSE) and yum (e.g. CentOS) based systems.} maintainers nomaintainer license GPL categories sysutils version 0.9.0 revision 0
